    {
      "instruction": "<p>Sprinkle your <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika</strong> and <strong>ground allspice</strong> over the hake and cook for 3-4 min on each side or until cooked through and blackened</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
