    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) with your <strong>mayo</strong>, a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> and 1 tsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> [2 tsp]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>in a small bowl – this is your <strong>chipotle mayo</strong></p>",
