    {
      "instruction": "<p>Load up the <strong>warmed tortillas </strong>with the <strong>blackened hake chunks</strong>, <strong>speedy pineapple salsa</strong> and <strong>shredded lettuce</strong></p><p>Dollop over the <strong>chipotle mayo</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
